    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AdminDashboardController
    JavaFX controller for the admin dashboard window.
    AdminDashboardStatsService
    Service for admin dashboard statistics.
    AdminUserInitializer
    Initializes default roles, permissions, and users if database is empty.
    AppPaths
    Computes OS-appropriate, user-writable locations for application data.
    AuthService
    Authentication helper service used by the desktop login flow.
    BackupScheduler
    Runs an automatic daily backup on startup.
    BackupService
    Creates and restores encrypted backups.
    BackupSettingsController
    Backup/Restore settings window.
    BackupSettingsService
    Stores backup settings for the desktop app.
    BrandingService
    Centralizes whitelabel branding and lab profile information.
    CategoryManagementController
    Controller for managing Department records (labeled as categories in parts of the UI).

    Entity representing a commission ledger entry for a lab order and doctor.
    CommissionLedgerRepository
    Repository interface for CommissionLedger entities, providing queries for commission tracking.
    CommissionManagementController
    Controller for Commission Management.
    ConfigService
    Service to manage system configuration settings.
    CreateOrderController
    JavaFX controller for creating lab orders.
    CurrentUserProvider
    Provides the current username for audit stamping.
    DashboardNavigator
    Handles navigation between login and dashboards.
    DashboardSwitchService
     
    DashboardType
    Enum defining all available dashboard types in the system.
    DataSeeder
    Seeds baseline master data into a fresh database on application startup.

    Department (also used as a "category" in the UI) that groups related TestDefinition and Panel entries.
    DepartmentRepository
    Repository for Department master data.
    DesktopApplication
    JavaFX Desktop Application entry point.
    DesktopCryptoConfig
    Desktop-only crypto configuration.
    DesktopCurrentUserProvider
    Desktop implementation backed by SessionManager.
    Doctor
    Entity representing a doctor and their commission details.
    DoctorCommissionLedgerController
    Controller that summarizes doctor commissions over a date range and exposes aggregate paid/due totals.
    DoctorCommissionLedgerController.DoctorCommissionSummary
    Immutable table row for doctor commission aggregates.
    DoctorPanelController
    Controller for the Doctor Management Panel.
    DoctorRepository
    Repository interface for Doctor entities, providing standard CRUD operations.
    ExpenseController
    Controller for recording operational expenses and querying them over a date range.
    FinanceTransaction
    Unified financial transaction view model used by reporting screens that merge income and expense sources into a single timeline.
    FinancialCategorySummary
    Aggregate row used by the financial queries screen to summarize counts and totals by category and type.
    FinancialQueriesController
    Controller for financial reporting queries.
    IdGenerator
    Utility class for generating unique Medical Record Numbers (MRN).
    InventoryItem
    Entity representing an inventory item and its stock details.
    InventoryItemFormController
    Form controller for creating and editing InventoryItem records.
    InventoryItemRepository
    Repository interface for InventoryItem entities, providing stock management queries.
    InventoryViewController
    JavaFX controller for inventory management view.
    LabDashboardController
    JavaFX controller for the lab technician dashboard window.
    LabInfo
    Entity representing laboratory information and contact details.
    LabInfoRepository
    Repository interface for LabInfo entity, providing access to laboratory configuration settings.
    LabOrder
    Entity representing a laboratory order, including patient, doctor, billing, and result details.
    LabOrderRepository
    Repository interface for LabOrder entities, providing CRUD operations and custom queries for dashboard statistics and patient order history.
    LabResult
    Entity representing a laboratory test result, including value, abnormality, remarks, and audit trail.
    LabResultRepository
    Repository interface for LabResult entities, providing CRUD operations for lab test results.
    LabWorklistController
    JavaFX controller for lab worklist.
    LocaleFormatService
    Locale-aware formatting helper for dates, times, and currency.
    LogoutUtil
    UI helper for session-scoped logout actions that close the tab containing a given node after user confirmation.
    MainController
    Controller for the main desktop shell.
    MainWindowController
    Controller for the main application window with tabbed interface.
    MasterDataSeeder
    Seeds master data on first run for production profile.

    OrderRequest
    DTO for creating a new lab order request.
    OrderService
    Service for handling lab order creation and related business logic.
    Panel
    A billable panel that groups multiple TestDefinition items under a single name.
    PanelRepository
    Repository for Panel entities.
    PasswordPolicyService
    Centralized password policy for the desktop application.
    Patient
    Entity representing a patient, including demographic and registration details.
    PatientRegistrationController
    JavaFX controller for patient registration.
    PatientRepository
    Repository for Patient registration and search operations.
    PatientService
    Service for handling patient registration and related logic.
    Payment
    Entity representing a general financial payment or expense.
    PaymentHistoryController
    Controller for Payment History.
    PaymentRepository
    Repository for miscellaneous income and expense Payment entries.
    Permission
    Entity representing a granular permission (e.g., PATIENT_CREATE, TEST_APPROVE).
    PermissionRepository
    Repository interface for Permission entities.
    PurchaseItemDTO
    DTO for representing a purchase item in an order.
    PurchaseRequest
    DTO for creating a new purchase request.
    PurchaseService
    Service for handling inventory purchases and supplier ledger updates.
    QdcLimsApplication
    Main entry point for the LIMS Spring Boot application.
    QrCodeUtil
    Utility class for generating QR codes as Base64-encoded PNG images.
    ReceptionDashboardController
    Controller for the Reception Dashboard.
    ReferenceRange
    Entity representing age and gender-specific reference ranges for lab test results.
    ReferenceRangeController
    Controller for managing gender and age-specific ReferenceRange entries for a selected TestDefinition.
    ReferenceRangeRepository
    Repository interface for ReferenceRange entities, providing CRUD operations for test reference ranges.
    ReportExportService
     
    ReportService
    Generates printable PDF lab reports for completed orders.
    ResultEntryController
    JavaFX controller for entering test results.
    ResultEntryRequest
    DTO for entering a lab result value.
    ResultService
    Service for handling lab result entry, validation, and saving logic.
    RevenueReportsController
    Controller for Revenue Reports.
    Role
    Entity representing a user role (e.g., ADMIN, RECEPTIONIST, LAB_TECHNICIAN).
    RoleRepository
    Repository interface for Role entities.
    SessionManager
    Session manager supporting multiple simultaneous user sessions.
    SessionManager.UserSession
    Session data for a single window.
    SessionTimeoutConfig
    Spring configuration that applies the session timeout to the desktop UI SessionManager at startup.
    Supplier
    Entity representing a supplier from whom inventory items are purchased.
    SupplierLedger
    Entity representing a financial ledger entry for tracking purchases from and payments to suppliers.
    SupplierLedgerRepository
    Repository interface for SupplierLedger entities, providing queries for supplier transaction history.
    SupplierManagementController
    Controller for maintaining supplier master data.
    SupplierPayablesController
    Controller that summarizes supplier bills, payments, and outstanding dues over a date range.
    SupplierPayablesController.SupplierPayableSummary
    Immutable table row for supplier payable aggregates.
    SupplierRepository
    Repository interface for Supplier entities, providing standard CRUD operations.
    SystemConfiguration
    Key-value system configuration entry used by the desktop settings screen.
    SystemConfigurationRepository
    Repository for key-value SystemConfiguration entries.
    SystemSettingsController
    Controller for the system settings screen backed by ConfigService key-value configuration entries.
    TestCategory
    Legacy/alternate test category entity.
    TestCategoryRepository
    Repository for TestCategory entries.
    TestConsumption
    Entity representing a recipe that links a test to inventory items and their required quantities.
    TestConsumptionRepository
    Repository interface for TestConsumption entities, providing recipe lookup for inventory management.
    TestDataInitializer
    Initializes financial test data for the LIMS application.
    TestDefinition
    Master data definition for a laboratory test, including pricing, reference-range metadata, and relationships to departments and panels.
    TestDefinitionRepository
    Repository interface for TestDefinition entities, providing CRUD operations and custom queries.
    TestDefinitionsController
    Controller for browsing, searching, and maintaining TestDefinition master data.
    TestDefinitionService
    Application service for managing TestDefinition master data used by the desktop UI.
    TestRecipe
    Represents the consumption recipe for a test.
    TestRecipeController
    Controller for defining per-test inventory consumption recipes.
    TestRecipeMigrationConfig
    Migrates legacy test recipe rows into the active test_consumption table.
    TestRecipeRepository
    Repository for TestRecipe definitions that describe inventory consumption per test.
    User
    Entity representing a system user with authentication credentials and role-based access.
    UserManagementController
    JavaFX controller for user management (Admin only).
    UserRepository
    Repository interface for User entities, providing authentication-related queries.
    UserService
    Service for user management and authentication.
    WindowSession
    Represents a user session tied to a specific window.
    WindowSessionManager
    Manages multiple window sessions, allowing different users to be logged in simultaneously in different windows on the same computer.
